precis:
Order (a) accepting the transfer from the Province of SASKATCHEWAN of the
administration and control over some 10,560 acres of land, and (b) setting
them apart for the use and benefit of the ISLAND LAKE (MINISTIKWAN) BAND OF
INDIANS as an addition to Island Lake Indian Reserve No. 161, which is
located near Loon Lake, Saskatchewan.
